sentences.sentence: Your ob-gyn or midwife is also a good resource.
sentences.translation: 你的妇产科医师或助产师也是一个好的资源。

sentences.sentence: Some women prefer to work with a midwife others prefer their ob-gyn.
sentences.translation: 一些女性喜欢寻求助产士的帮助，其他人则喜欢找妇科医生。

sentences.sentence: Age may be one of the most important factors in discussing GYN pathology cases.
sentences.translation: 异常细胞等，年龄是妇科病例讨论中最重要的因素之一。
